    somebody\r\nI wanna feel the \nheat \nwith somebody\r\nYeah, I wanna dance with
    somebody\r\nWith somebody who loves me\r\nOh, I wanna dance with somebody\r\nI
    wanna feel the heat with somebody\r\nYeah, I wanna dance with somebody\r\nWith
    somebody who \nloves \nme"
